text: Is the youth exhibiting changes in eating habits?
Does the youth have mood swings?
Has the youth experienced seemingly unexplained changes in sleep pattern?
Has the youth recently run away from home?
Has there been a significant change in the youth's relationships with peers, and/or attendance at social events?
Does the youth appear easily startled or jumpy?
Have you noticed unexplained marks or bruises on the youth's body?
Has the youth been missing more school?
Have you noticed signs of self-harm?
Have you noticed frequent signs of intoxication due to either drugs or alcohol?
Has the youth recently began coming home at late or at inconsitent hours without willingness to share the reason?
Does the youth have unexplained gifts or money?
Does the youth's significant other control his or her behavior?
Has the youth changed their wardrobe to be more provocative?
Does the youth have a new job about which they are hesitant to share details?
Has the youth been wearing unintentionally dirty or damaged clothing?
Does the youth's family seem disinterested or uninvolved in the child's life?
Does the youth appear malnourished or frequently try to take home food?
Has the youth been acting out in public against either peers or authority?
Has the child been engaging in bullying behaviors?
